#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn14.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn14.16:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 14 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 14 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn14.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 16. Sagāthāsutta → sagāthasuttaṃ (bj, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn14.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Sagāthāsutta "
msgstr "16. With Verses "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn14.16:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn14.16:1.2"
msgid "“Dhātusova, bhikkhave, sattā saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:1.3"
msgid "Hīnādhimuttikā hīnādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "Those who have a bad attitude come together and converge with those who have a bad attitude. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:1.4"
msgid "Atītampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandiṃsu samiṃsu. "
msgstr "In the past … "

msgctxt "sn14.16:1.5"
msgid "Hīnādhimuttikā hīnādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandiṃsu samiṃsu. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn14.16:2.1"
msgid "Anāgatampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandissanti samessanti. "
msgstr "In the future … "

msgctxt "sn14.16:2.2"
msgid "Hīnādhimuttikā hīnādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandissanti samessanti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn14.16:3.1"
msgid "Etarahipi kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannaṃ addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "At present, too, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:3.2"
msgid "Hīnādhimuttikā hīnādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "Those who have a bad attitude come together and converge with those who have a bad attitude. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn14.16:4.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gūtho gūthena saṃsandati sameti; "
msgstr "It’s like how dung comes together with dung, "

msgctxt "sn14.16:4.2"
msgid "muttaṃ muttena saṃsandati sameti; "
msgstr "urine with urine, "

msgctxt "sn14.16:4.3"
msgid "kheḷo kheḷena saṃsandati sameti; "
msgstr "spit with spit, "

msgctxt "sn14.16:4.4"
msgid "pubbo pubbena saṃsandati sameti; "
msgstr "pus with pus, "

msgctxt "sn14.16:4.5"
msgid "lohitaṃ lohitena saṃsandati sameti; "
msgstr "and blood with blood. "

#. VAR: dhātusova → sabbatthapi evameva
msgctxt "sn14.16:4.6"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, dhātusova sattā saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "In the same way, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:4.7"
msgid "Hīnādhimuttikā hīnādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "Those who have a bad attitude come together and converge with those who have a bad attitude. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:4.8"
msgid "Atītampi kho addhānaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "In the past … "

msgctxt "sn14.16:4.9"
msgid "anāgatampi kho addhānaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "In the future … "

msgctxt "sn14.16:4.10"
msgid "etarahipi kho paccuppannaṃ addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "At present, too, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:4.11"
msgid "Hīnādhimuttikā hīnādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "Those who have a bad attitude come together and converge with those who have a bad attitude. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.158, sc5
msgctxt "sn14.16:5.1"
msgid "Dhātusova, bhikkhave, sattā saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "Sentient beings come together and converge because of an element. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:5.2"
msgid "Kalyāṇādhimuttikā kalyāṇādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "Those who have a good attitude come together and converge with those who have a good attitude. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:5.3"
msgid "Atītampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandiṃsu samiṃsu. "
msgstr "In the past … "

msgctxt "sn14.16:5.4"
msgid "Kalyāṇādhimuttikā kalyāṇādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandiṃsu samiṃsu. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn14.16:6.1"
msgid "Anāgatampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "In the future … "

msgctxt "sn14.16:6.2"
msgid "etarahipi kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannaṃ addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "At present, too, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:6.3"
msgid "Kalyāṇādhimuttikā kalyāṇādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "Those who have a good attitude come together and converge with those who have a good attitude. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn14.16:7.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, khīraṃ khīrena saṃsandati sameti; "
msgstr "It’s like how milk comes together with milk, "

msgctxt "sn14.16:7.2"
msgid "telaṃ telena saṃsandati sameti; "
msgstr "oil with oil, "

msgctxt "sn14.16:7.3"
msgid "sappi sappinā saṃsandati sameti; "
msgstr "ghee with ghee, "

msgctxt "sn14.16:7.4"
msgid "madhu madhunā saṃsandati sameti; "
msgstr "honey with honey, "

msgctxt "sn14.16:7.5"
msgid "phāṇitaṃ phāṇitena saṃsandati sameti; "
msgstr "and molasses with molasses. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:7.6"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, dhātusova sattā saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "In the same way, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:7.7"
msgid "Kalyāṇādhimuttikā kalyāṇādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "Those who have a good attitude come together and converge with those who have a good attitude. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:7.8"
msgid "Atītampi kho addhānaṃ … "
msgstr "In the past … "

msgctxt "sn14.16:7.9"
msgid "anāgatampi kho addhānaṃ … "
msgstr "In the future … "

msgctxt "sn14.16:7.10"
msgid "etarahipi kho paccuppannaṃ addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "At present, too, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:7.11"
msgid "Kalyāṇādhimuttikā kalyāṇādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samentī”ti. "
msgstr "Those who have a good attitude come together and converge with those who have a good attitude.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn14.16:8.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn14.16:8.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: "
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "

# NOTE: BB’s “woods of lust” is barely comprehensible, and suggests a crude and presumably unintended pun. Mostly, as here, vanatha is used in ways that don’t rely on the metaphorical basis, so there’s no need to resort to such means.sc9
#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "sn14.16:8.3"
msgid "“Saṃsaggā vanatho jāto, "
msgstr "“Socializing promotes entanglement; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn14.16:8.4"
msgid "asaṃsaggena chijjati; "
msgstr "they’re cut off by being aloof. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn14.16:8.5"
msgid "Parittaṃ dārumāruyha, "
msgstr "If you’re lost in the middle of a great sea, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn14.16:8.6"
msgid "yathā sīde mahaṇṇave. "
msgstr "and you clamber up on a little log, you’ll sink. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "sn14.16:10.1"
msgid "Evaṃ kusītamāgamma, "
msgstr "So too, a person who lives well "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn14.16:10.2"
msgid "sādhujīvipi sīdati; "
msgstr "sinks by relying on a lazy person. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn14.16:10.3"
msgid "Tasmā taṃ parivajjeyya, "
msgstr "Hence you should avoid such "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn14.16:10.4"
msgid "kusītaṃ hīnavīriyaṃ. "
msgstr "a lazy person who lacks energy. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn14.16:11.1"
msgid "Pavivittehi ariyehi, "
msgstr "Dwell with the noble ones "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: jhāyīhi → jhāyihi (bj) | jhāyibhi (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn14.16:11.2"
msgid "pahitattehi jhāyīhi; "
msgstr "who are secluded and determined "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn14.16:11.3"
msgid "Niccaṃ āraddhavīriyehi, "
msgstr "and always energetic; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn14.16:11.4"
msgid "paṇḍitehi sahāvase”ti. "
msgstr "the astute who practice absorption.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn14.16:11.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
